{"tid":2463024,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎一人一email去信倫敦Kingston University撤除Eason榮譽博士名銜","createTime":"2021-03-26T11:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T22:43:23.000Z","uid":189150,"like":237,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"cbb90e80b8a83a8512aed41c6cdd88bedc0fe520","tid":2463024,"uid":189150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:26:49.000Z","msg":"林鄭都放棄左劍橋榮譽院士學位喇，eason開到聲支持種族滅絕唔係仲可以叫自已做英國榮譽博士呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望各位一人一信令kingston university 回應<br />\n下面封email我尋晚手快快打既，各位巴絲打幫手改改文 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你鍾意既成段重寫都得，本人任插唔嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有兩位巴絲打已經幫手改返岩d grammar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔該晒各位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後改完一齊send去kingston大學既PR media inquiry同埋學生組織要求跟進<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kingston.ac.uk/contact-us/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingston.ac.uk%2Fcontact-us%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=3fb91e2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kingston.ac.uk/contact-us/</a><br />\nUnion of Kingston Students<br />\n    Tel: +44 (0)20 8417 2868<br />\n    Email: studentsunion@kingston.ac.uk<br />\nMedia Enquiry<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.kingston.ac.uk/enquiries/337/media-enquiry-form/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kingston.ac.uk%2Fenquiries%2F337%2Fmedia-enquiry-form%2F&d=qOmKSCuv03M2cFfeadZVWpzZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=8a4c897e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.kingston.ac.uk/enquiries/337/media-enquiry-form/</a><br />\n<br />\n其實我都唔知呢d信應該send去邊<br />\n點樣send比校長或者音樂系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  有心既巴打可以幫手搵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------- Email 稿 ----------------------------<br />\n<br />\nDear Sir / Madam,<br />\n<br />\n<ins>Rescind Eason Chan's Honorary Degree</ins><br />\n<br />\nIn 2014, Eason Chan was awarded an honorary doctorate degree by Kingston University for his achievement in his music career. Unfortunately, fast-forward to 2021, the current values and political stance Eason Chan displays on social media stand against everything Kingston University represents.<br />\n<br />\nWhile retail giants such as Nike and H&amp;M are currently facing a backlash in China after they expressed concern about the alleged use of Uighur forced labour in cotton production, Eason Chan, a well-respected celebrity in China, stood up for the Chinese government and publicly condemned these companies for &quot;boycotting Xinjiang cotton&quot; and &quot;stigmatizing china&quot;. Eason Chan and his company released a written statement today endorsing the use of Xinjiang cotton, cutting ties with the retail giants that he endorsed, and unilaterally terminating the contract with Adidas as the brand spokesperson.<br />\n<br />\nDespite China still denies genocide charges, many proofs, and evidence show that China has committed serious human rights violations against the Uighur Muslim minority in the Xinjiang autonomous region. We believe that Kingston University is first and foremost an educational institution in the UK, committed to developing future leaders that will work together to create a better and safer society for mankind. Allowing Eason Chan to retain his honorary doctorate represents a hollow and superficial ideological commitment from Kingston to these principles. Therefore, Eason Chan does not deserve to bear the distinction of an honorary degree from Kingston. To suggest otherwise would ignore and minimize the work of Kingston's community and graduates to promote diversity, inclusion, and human rights.<br />\n<br />\nYours sincerely,<br />\n連登仔<br />\n<br />\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------------"},{"pid":"fde735ff3415f7e2d32bccc390333e646d6a7760","tid":2463024,"uid":297997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:27:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"439942f2e065cb5161c258925ff3e0f2030941df","tid":2463024,"uid":205232,"like":5,"dislike":80,"score":-75,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"救李宇軒好過啦 浪費資源 手足不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4f0b7cc4ee3e65f0e1e37f53a304ef82249f40f","tid":2463024,"uid":174512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:32:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7eda0fc55814fca4b035351e7851b4f793607dbd","tid":2463024,"uid":141901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:32:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"64279061085f7afff38a69a937a43e5e1d52eb66","tid":2463024,"uid":10757,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"quote":{"pid":"439942f2e065cb5161c258925ff3e0f2030941df","tid":2463024,"uid":205232,"like":5,"dislike":80,"score":-75,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:31:53.000Z","msg":"救李宇軒好過啦 浪費資源 手足不是condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T11:35:06.000Z","msg":"Sd封信哂你電定幾秒網絡費用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2739b6cda3617dcf85f9517c65f01895c5cba773","tid":2463024,"uid":76470,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"439942f2e065cb5161c258925ff3e0f2030941